@test("It should show colored diff in passthrough mode with --colors")
@given("file", filename="some-test.test")

@@test("A failure test")
@@given("file")
@@whenRun("./bin/jcunit")
@@expectOutput("stdout")
Some output
@@endtest

@whenRun("./bin/jcunit", args="--colors")
@expectOutput("stdout")
F                                                  (100%)

There are 1 failures:

1) some-test.test : A failure test
--- Expected
+++ Actual
[31m-Some output[0m
[32m+No tests executed![0m

Passed: 0, Skipped: 0, Errors: 0, [31mFailed: 1[0m, Incomplete: 0

@endtest

@test("It should show no colors in diff without --colors flag")
@given("file", filename="some-test.test")

@@test("A failure test")
@@given("file")
@@whenRun("./bin/jcunit")
@@expectOutput("stdout")
